column5: Great report as ususal G.  Joey
nicely done, was this taken in July?    what beautiful weather! WTG!
Nice batch or crappies there Glen - bet they're gonna taste real good!   Thanks for the post   Don
nice report & pics glen,i wish i got to go out in my boat today  well looks like you will be having a fresh fish fry tonight   cheers
Nice catch. My crappy hunt wasn't so successful today  Ah well there's always next time
Nice report Glen very crappie is better than being skunked.Nice bass.Love the Redneck news.Your almost wearing that candian T-shirt.
Soon that sign will say "no topless rednecks"  I imagine you are still cleaning or enjoying a feast right about now.  Say fella, Where's the dam?

Glen, nice mess of fish again bud,and looks as if they had thier stomachs full to,and a spotted bass to boot.we don,t have any of those up here in... CANADA...have yourself a fine feed Glen TTYL.  Steve
I see pondered over the correct placement of each fish for the photo. No sloppy mess of fish pics there. Thanks for showing us those nice fish.
Nice fish Glen. Congrats and I hope you enjoyed the fish fry.
I only ever ate crappies once Glen, but they sure were tasty....now I'm envious !!
Nice haul GCD, the parking at the ramp looks full, I guess a few other boats on the water. Good report and pic's...
Well done Bama, thanks for sharing!  Whopper
Nice mess of fish there Glen...Enjoy !!!
Nice little haul there.  Do you have a cold...I noticed your wearing a shirt?
Another nice report, gcd.  Of course, I think any report where you ain't nekkid is a good one...    Mike
Attaboy, Glen.  Thanks for the pictures.
